    </div>
    
    <div class="col-12 col-sm-7 offset-sm-1">
      <h2 class="text-center">Final Fantasy Tactics</h2>
      <br />
      <p>
        Final Fantasy Tactics is a side series and in my opinion is the best game in the franchise. The gameplay is perfect. The story is perfect. The story really keeps you guessing and surprised. The story of this game kinda reminds me of Game of Thrones and there are numerous sides and fighting for different ends. This game is definitley a 100 and I have played it several times.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
